  ss:{dna:'Voice, acoustic guitar, emotional truth, first-person narrative, autobiographical imagery. The song is the diary entry.',structure:'Most flexible genre. Verse-only (no chorus), VCVCBC, or through-composed. The STORY determines structure â€” not a template.',suno:'"fingerpicked acoustic guitar, intimate close-mic vocals, warm room reverb, no drums" for stripped. Add "brushed snare, upright bass" for fuller feel.',keys:['Every line must earn its place â€” no filler','Specificity creates universality â€” house numbers, dog names, street names','Second verse must deepen emotionally, not repeat the first','Guitar tuning is a character â€” mention DADGAD or open G in style'],artists:'Tracy Chapman آ· Joni Mitchell آ· Elliott Smith آ· Bon Iver آ· Phoebe Bridgers آ· Paul Simon آ· Brandi Carlile'},
