          <a href="https://console.anthropic.com" target="_blank"
             style="color:var(--amber);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">console.anthropic.com</a>
          â€” it only takes 2 minutes.<br>
          <span style="color:var(--tx4)">Your key is stored locally in your browser only.</span>
        </div>

        ${errorMsg ? `<div style="background:var(--redbg);border:1px solid var(--redline);border-radius:var(--r2);padding:8px 12px;font-size:12px;color:var(--red);margin-bottom:14px">${errorMsg}</div>` : ''}

